    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic and well-maintained ride! It\u2019s in great shape and has been clearly cared for, offering a smooth, dependable driving experience you'll love. While you might find a few minor signs of character from regular use, the overall condition is impressive and it's ready for many more miles of adventure. This is a solid, honest car that looks sharp and performs beautifully!",
