      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle exhibits a flawless exterior finish complemented by an interior that remains in pristine showroom condition. Mechanically peerless and rigorously inspected, it represents the pinnacle of its class, offering an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
